32:09.228 --> 32:11.797
- Father?

32:11.797 --> 32:13.565
- What are you doing here?
Get out.

32:13.565 --> 32:14.900
- Wait, please.

32:14.900 --> 32:17.136
- I have nothing
to say to you or anyone.

32:17.136 --> 32:18.504
- Father, I'm a Catholic,

32:18.504 --> 32:21.773
and I have something
I need to say to you.

32:21.773 --> 32:25.811
Do you think you could
listen to me, please?

32:25.811 --> 32:28.814
I was born and raised
in the Church.

32:28.814 --> 32:32.184
I got two cousins
who, uh, who are priests.

32:32.184 --> 32:34.920
I even thought that
I'd become one myself.

32:34.920 --> 32:38.257
To me, there was
no higher calling.

32:38.257 --> 32:40.426
- Mm, mm.
Then I can imagine

32:40.426 --> 32:43.095
what you must think
of the Church and me.

32:43.095 --> 32:46.532
- No.
No, you can't.

32:46.532 --> 32:50.169
I still go to Mass
every Sunday.

32:50.169 --> 32:52.838
During this case,
I've been doing twice a week.

32:55.941 --> 32:57.443
- What is it you want?

32:57.443 --> 33:02.081
- I want you to think
about Eugene as a kid,

33:02.081 --> 33:04.883
about why you wanted
to become a priest

33:04.883 --> 33:07.586
in the first place.

33:07.586 --> 33:11.557
- Those memories...
[murmurs]

33:11.557 --> 33:13.225
they're lost to me.

33:13.225 --> 33:16.328
- No.
I saw you praying, Father.

33:18.764 --> 33:22.268
You still believe in God,
don't you?

33:22.268 --> 33:24.370
Well, He's here.

33:24.370 --> 33:25.771
I know that you feel Him.

33:25.771 --> 33:27.106
- If He is,

33:27.106 --> 33:31.077
